parameters: This must be the place he spoke of.
I thought it might have something to do with the river...
maybe he took a different route.
This feels like déjà vu, doesn't it?
But the stakes seem higher this time.
The herbs could be hidden anywhere.
(As \C[5]Maleena\c[0] suggested, I should roam around and inspect every bush and tree for the herbs listed on the paper \C[3]Elphaba\C[0] gave me.)
Come on, come on! Where is it?!
I don't have all day for this...!!?!
\n[1], look! I think I've found it!
Holy cow, you found them so fast!
How are you able to do that!??
Hehe, well I'm in the forest all the time,
and sometimes need some herbs too.
Wow, can you teach me sometime?
Your expertise shines through yet again!
The forest is a second home to me, and its secrets, like these herbs, are friends I visit often.
You've got to share your secret with me, \C[5]Maleena\c[0]!
The knowledge of the forest is a gift to be shared.
Let's get to the next area.
(Let's keep our focus on finding the herb and try not to disturb \C[5]Maleena\c[0] in her search.)
